# The milestone-2 round trip: two driver clicks (stamping groups,
# items, and the When), one click on the most recently stamped remove
# button, and the status label proves the whole loop — stamping, tags,
# data-addressed removal, and the answering signal write.
settle 1500
click button#0
settle 400
click button#0
settle 400
click button#last
settle 700
expect label#0 "removed g2/a, 0 left"
